    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at CGI India Capital India. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Senior Software Engineer to strengthen our Ahmedabad-based team.\n\nAbout CGI India Capital India:\nCGI India Capital India is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in Python\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ahmedabad, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with CGI India Capital India!",
